## Gladiators 资产包使用指南（K12横版2D格斗游戏）

### 资产包路径
所有资产位于 `assets/gladiators/` 下。

---

### 一、角色系统（核心）

#### 角色分配（PRD：2个可选角色 + 1个AI角色）
| 角色ID | 路径 | 风格 | 用途 |
|--------|------|------|------|
| Char1 | PNG/Characters/Char1/ | 蓝色机甲骑士（红色马尾） | 玩家可选角色1 |
| Char2 | PNG/Characters/Char2/ | 橄榄色骑士 | 玩家可选角色2 |
| Char3 | PNG/Characters/Char3/ | 红羽骑士 | AI专用角色 |

#### 动画列表（每个角色均有以下动画）
| 动画名 | 文件夹 | 帧数 | 用途 |
|--------|--------|------|------|
| idle | Idle | 10帧 | 待机（循环） |
| walk | Walk | 18帧 | 移动（循环） |
| hit | Hit | 22帧 | 轻拳攻击（含帧感三阶段） |
| gethit | GetHit | 14帧 | 受击反馈 |
| defense | Defense | 14帧 | 格挡（K键按住循环） |
| death | Death | 35帧 | 死亡（HP归零） |
| opening | Opening | 14帧 | 开场动画 |

#### 帧文件命名规则
```
PNG/Characters/{Char1|Char2|Char3}/{AnimFolder}/skeleton-{AnimName}_{i}.png
例：PNG/Characters/Char1/Hit/skeleton-Hit_0.png ~ skeleton-Hit_21.png
```

---

### 二、Phaser.js 加载代码（preload 阶段）

```javascript
// 1. 加载背景
this.load.image('bg_battle', 'assets/gladiators/PNG/Backgrounds/BG1/Full.png');

// 2. 加载UI
this.load.image('ui_knight1',  'assets/gladiators/PNG/Ui/Knight1.png');
this.load.image('ui_knight2',  'assets/gladiators/PNG/Ui/Knight2.png');
this.load.image('ui_btn_start','assets/gladiators/PNG/Ui/Button1.png');
this.load.image('ui_btn_replay','assets/gladiators/PNG/Ui/Button2.png');
this.load.image('ui_hp_bg',    'assets/gladiators/PNG/Ui/Healthpoint_bg.png');
this.load.image('ui_hp_green', 'assets/gladiators/PNG/Ui/GreenHp.png');
this.load.image('ui_hp_enemy', 'assets/gladiators/PNG/Ui/EnemyHpbar.png');
this.load.image('ui_win',      'assets/gladiators/PNG/Ui/WinBar.png');
this.load.image('ui_defeat',   'assets/gladiators/PNG/Ui/DefeatBar.png');
this.load.image('ui_popup',    'assets/gladiators/PNG/Ui/popupBox.png');

// 3. 加载角色逐帧动画（Char1/Char2/Char3）
const CHARS = ['Char1', 'Char2', 'Char3'];
const ANIMS = { Idle:10, Walk:18, Hit:22, GetHit:14, Defense:14, Death:35, Opening:14 };
CHARS.forEach(char => {
  Object.entries(ANIMS).forEach(([anim, count]) => {
    for (let i = 0; i < count; i++) {
      this.load.image(
        `${char.toLowerCase()}_${anim.toLowerCase()}_${i}`,
        `assets/gladiators/PNG/Characters/${char}/${anim}/skeleton-${anim}_${i}.png`
      );
    }
  });
});
```

---

### 三、注册动画（create 阶段）

```javascript
const CHARS = ['Char1', 'Char2', 'Char3'];
const ANIM_DEFS = [
  { name:'idle',    folder:'Idle',    frames:10, fps:10, repeat:-1 },
  { name:'walk',    folder:'Walk',    frames:18, fps:12, repeat:-1 },
  { name:'hit',     folder:'Hit',     frames:22, fps:18, repeat:0  },
  { name:'gethit',  folder:'GetHit',  frames:14, fps:14, repeat:0  },
  { name:'defense', folder:'Defense', frames:14, fps:12, repeat:-1 },
  { name:'death',   folder:'Death',   frames:35, fps:12, repeat:0  },
  { name:'opening', folder:'Opening', frames:14, fps:12, repeat:0  }
];
CHARS.forEach(char => {
  const c = char.toLowerCase();
  ANIM_DEFS.forEach(def => {
    this.anims.create({
      key: `${c}_${def.name}`,
      frames: Array.from({ length: def.frames }, (_, i) => ({ key: `${c}_${def.name}_${i}` })),
      frameRate: def.fps,
      repeat: def.repeat
    });
  });
});
```

---

### 四、角色精灵使用示例

```javascript
// 创建玩家精灵（使用第一帧初始化）
const player = this.add.sprite(300, 400, 'char1_idle_0');
player.play('char1_idle');

// 攻击（J键）
player.play('char1_hit');
player.once('animationcomplete', () => player.play('char1_idle'));

// 格挡（K键按下）
player.play('char1_defense');
// K键松开
player.play('char1_idle');

// 受击 + 闪白效果
player.play('char1_gethit');
player.setTint(0xffffff);
this.time.delayedCall(100, () => player.clearTint());

// 死亡
player.play('char1_death');
player.once('animationcomplete', () => { /* 跳转结算页面 */ });

// AI角色（右侧，水平翻转）
const ai = this.add.sprite(700, 400, 'char3_idle_0').setFlipX(true);
ai.play('char3_idle');
```

---

### 五、攻击帧感三阶段判定（Hit动画 22帧）

```javascript
// startup: 帧0-6  （前32%，攻击准备，无伤害判定）
// active:  帧7-14 （中间36%，攻击判定生效）
// recovery:帧15-21（后32%，恢复阶段）
player.on('animationupdate', (anim, frame) => {
  if (anim.key === 'char1_hit') {
    const fi = frame.index - 1; // Phaser帧index从1开始
    if (fi >= 7 && fi <= 14) {
      checkHit(player, enemy); // active阶段检测命中
    }
  }
});
```

---

### 六、血条实现

```javascript
const hpBg   = this.add.image(200, 40, 'ui_hp_bg');
const hpFill = this.add.image(hpBg.x - hpBg.width/2, 40, 'ui_hp_green').setOrigin(0, 0.5);
const maxHp  = 100;
function updateHp(newHp) {
  hpFill.scaleX = Math.max(0, newHp) / maxHp;
}
```

---

### 七、PRD页面资产速查

| 页面 | 资产Key | 说明 |
|------|---------|------|
| 角色选择 | `ui_knight1`, `ui_knight2` | 角色头像展示 |
| 角色选择 | `ui_btn_start` (Button1.png) | 「开始对战」金黄色按钮 |
| 对战 | `bg_battle` (BG1/Full.png) | 沙漠峡谷擂台背景 |
| 对战 | `ui_hp_bg`, `ui_hp_green` | 玩家血条 |
| 对战 | `ui_hp_enemy` | 敌人血条 |
| 结算 | `ui_win` (WinBar.png) | 胜利横幅 |
| 结算 | `ui_defeat` (DefeatBar.png) | 失败横幅 |
| 结算 | `ui_popup` (popupBox.png) | 结算弹出框 |
| 结算 | `ui_btn_replay` (Button2.png) | 「再来一局」绿色按钮 |

---

### 注意事项
1. **逐帧PNG加载量较大**：3个角色 × 7种动画 = 约 (10+18+22+14+14+35+14)×3 = 381 张图片，建议在 preload 场景统一加载并显示进度条。
2. **AI角色翻转**：AI角色在右侧，需 `setFlipX(true)` 水平翻转面向玩家。
3. **动画key命名规则**：`{charN}_{animName}`，例如 `char1_hit`、`char2_defense`、`char3_idle`。
4. **帧key命名规则**：`{charN}_{animName}_{frameIndex}`，例如 `char1_hit_0`。
5. **Spine骨骼部件**（Spine/Char0X/Images/）：本PRD不需要使用，直接用PNG/Characters下的逐帧序列即可。

